  <h1>HoeFax Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> August 2025</p>

  <h2>Age Restriction</h2>
  <p>HoeFax is strictly for users 18 years and older. By using this app, you confirm you are at least 18. If you are under 18, please do not use or access HoeFax.</p>

  <h2>User Content Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>Users upload and share their own images and information on HoeFax. HoeFax does not review, endorse, or take responsibility for any user-generated content. You are solely responsible for what you post. We reserve the right to remove any content that violates laws or our guidelines.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect data you provide, such as profile details and images, plus usage data to improve the app.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To operate and improve HoeFax</li>
    <li>To communicate with users</li>
    <li>To comply with legal requirements</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share data with trusted service providers or when required by law.</p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information but cannot guarantee complete security.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You can update or delete your profile info anytime. To request data deletion, contact us.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Please check back regularly.</p>

